%F A059917 a(n) = a(n-1)*(3^(2^(n-1)) + 1) - 3^(2^(n-1)) = A059723(n+1)/A059723(n) = A059918(n) + 1 = a(n-1)*A059919(n-1) - A011764(n-1).
%F A059917 a(0) = 2; a(n) = ((2*a(n-1) - 1)^2 + 1)/2, n >= 1. - _Daniel Forgues_, Jun 22 2011
